casebody.data:
Florence STRONG and Barbara Roberts, Appellants, v. BROWARD COUNTY KENNEL CLUB, Inc., et al., Appellees. No. 12442. United States Court of Appeals Fifth Circuit. Oct. 11, 1948. No appearances entered for appellants. C. A. Hiassen, of Fort Lauderdale, Fla., for appellee.

Before HUTCHESON, Chief Judge and McCORD and WALLER, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Motion is sustained and the appeal is dismissed.
